title: Hour 3 - Chris Haynes (03-31-20)
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Chris Haynes (03-31-20)
description:
Jason Smith and Rob Parker fill in for Dan Patrick and have differing opinions on their interest level in watching classic games and speak with Yahoo Sports NBA insider Chris Haynes about the big decision weighing heavy on the shoulders of the NBA. Plus, Jason and Rob talk about the NCAA giving an extra year of eligibility to spring athletes!
